{"tid":2098471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果香港人捐錢去支援九州水災多過大陸會點？","createTime":"2020-07-07T13:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:50:03.000Z","uid":141400,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"06ff6732b56ca41ba38428118bb1252d36a98e7f","tid":2098471,"uid":141400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"一定會一地玻璃碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好捐錢去九州，因為捐錢俾黃絲就係支持攬炒、支持恐怖主義；捐錢俾小日本即係支持軍國主義。<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要照顧祖國十四億人民感情，如果香港人捐錢俾九州仲多過大陸幾廿倍，祖國會好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係中國人呀Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b398dfcfa4d1ad7d5041d0cf5c2494998c220198","tid":2098471,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9398bf1d542fb10439f3786e9d8ff853a884d85","tid":2098471,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"如果冇人攪籌款就冇計啦"},{"pid":"96cb69d03fd8252216de598e5dbd8f30a3902a05","tid":2098471,"uid":141400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b398dfcfa4d1ad7d5041d0cf5c2494998c220198","tid":2098471,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定唔可以</span></span>捐俾小日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a259f035df6f3d4a10d707db206ac37ab7de20